{"tid":818574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台駐大阪辦事處處長上吊亡　疑因未能及時助滯日台客捱批","createTime":"2018-09-14T08:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T08:15:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7da9b6e54c66033d59f0f99b7d935202c8eeeb0c","tid":818574,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"台灣駐大阪辦事處處長蘇啓誠今早（9月14日）在大阪住所上吊自殺身亡，懷疑事件與早前台灣旅客在日遇上颱風被迫滯留關西機場，駐大阪辦事處未能及時提供幫助而受各方指責有關。 對於61歲的蘇啓誠在日輕生，台灣總統蔡英文在Facebook表示感到非常悲痛跟不捨，已指示外交部全力協助蘇之家屬，妥善辦理相關後續事務。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文又呼嘯台灣各界，為所有在最前線的外交人員給予鼓勵。 早前颱風飛燕吹襲日本時，大阪關西機場受到重創，機場需要暫時關閉，多名旅客被迫滯留機場。當時有消息傳出中國駐日領使館派出專車接載中國旅客離開機場，台灣旅客只要認作中國人，也可以乘專車離開，但其後證實有關專車並非中國領使館安排，只是日本有關當局安排。"},{"pid":"7381198463682efbdc5c07733b62f35bd96a923e","tid":818574,"uid":52339,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"睇下香港班狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左事仲可以笑笑口咁射波"},{"pid":"4e152fc1a94414cc107bb8ea1aad2c28f59876eb","tid":818574,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f7a79aca9eda59aa8e211f44f444cecaffc738","tid":818574,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:10:25.000Z","msg":"其實未致於嚴重到要自殺下話"},{"pid":"5bd95e3a0157689a86120b508b0e99c18357d85f","tid":818574,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7381198463682efbdc5c07733b62f35bd96a923e","tid":818574,"uid":52339,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"睇下香港班狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左事仲可以笑笑口咁射波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201809/05/P2018090400668_photo_1142773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201809%2F05%2FP2018090400668_photo_1142773.jpg&h=edd3a44f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76333e12e385a09825468fb52dfbcc6d96f848f9","tid":818574,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"吊頸謝罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088446b810f4ceb7d5bdf6db9edd3a77b92d3e21","tid":818574,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"學左日本個套"}]}